						               													<description>From the site:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal Pro Soccer is a dice/chart/fast action card simulation of Pro Soccer. With this game, you can replay current MLS teams or English Premier League teams or seasons from the past. Witness such greats as Pele, Franz Beckenbauer, Clint Mathis, Landon Donovan, Carlos Valderamma, Sir Stanley Matthews, Johan Cruyff, Gordon Banks, Cobi Jones, Robbie Fowler, Michael Owen, Fabien Barthez, Tim Howard as they take the field on your tabletop. Play classic matchups such as the recent World Cup Final between Germany and Brazil....can Ronaldo repeat his two goal performance or can Oliver Kahn shut out the Brazilians and take the prize back to Germany???? Or replay the whole tournament and see if longshots such as Senegal, South Korea or the US can go all the way.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All the action is here....from the shots and goals, to highlight saves, to the fouls and bookings to corner kicks and a few wild events that make &amp;quot;The Beautiful Game&amp;quot;, the most popular game in the world. A game should take no more than 25 minutes once mastered and a whole tournament can be played out in a matter of a few weeks. Most of all, the game is FUN!!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Several months of developement plus over 50 playtest matches insure that Goal Pro Soccer is one of the most accurate simulations on the market.....best of all.....the price of the game???&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's FREE......Just download the components, print it out on cardstock and you have yourself a game worth playing for hours. It is FREEWARE so if you enjoy it, pass it along to another soccer fan or sports tablegaming buddy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
